             .withColumn('month', udf_month('date'))
            #  .withColumn('month', udf_month_ct('date'))

cldayslist = list(map(lambda d: Row(date=d), clean_days_list))
print(clean_days_list[:5])
print(cldayslist[:5])

clday = spark.createDataFrame(cldayslist)

%pyspark

from pyjake.sparkmodule import udf_month

sza = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///sun/kasi_sun_angle.parquet')\
           .withColumn('month', udf_month('date'))
sza.show()
sza.createOrReplaceTempView('sza')

%sql

select date, time, month, solar_zenith from sza
where date like '201_-__-01' and date < '2019-11-31' and solar_zenith <90
order by time
